[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man charged with murder of woman in Evesham

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been charged with the murder of a woman found dead at a house in Evesham, Worcestershire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 53-year-old woman, who has not been formally identified, was pronounced dead at the address in Bewdley Street on Friday.
She was found to have suffered a cardiac arrest after police were called at 05:48 BST.
Mark Pearce, 51, also of Bewdley Street, will appear at Worcester Crown Court on Tuesday.
